%% Sequence — cold turn (post-Phase-10)
%% Phase 1 + Phase 3 changes are highlighted: AppState key reuse + tokio::join! grounding.

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Operator
    participant Drawer as CopilotDrawer.svelte
    participant Routes as drive_native_sse
    participant State as AppState
    participant Grounding as gather_grounding
    participant Soul as SOUL helix
    participant Git as git_context
    participant Provider as OllamaCliProvider
    participant Cloud as Ollama Cloud

    Note over State: Phase 1: la_native_api_key read once at AppState::new()<br/>(eliminates per-request std::env::var TOCTOU)
    Operator->>Drawer: types message + Enter
    Drawer->>Routes: POST /api/builds/:id/copilot (HTTP SSE)
    Routes->>State: read la_native_api_key (Some)
    State-->>Routes: SecretString clone
    Note over Routes,Grounding: Phase 3: tokio::join!(soul_fut, git_fut)<br/>wall = max(soul_ms, git_ms), not sum
    par parallel grounding
        Routes->>Grounding: spawn soul_fut (400ms timeout)
        Grounding->>Soul: search (BM25 top-5)
        Soul-->>Grounding: results
    and
        Routes->>Grounding: spawn git_fut (800ms timeout)
        Grounding->>Git: branch + commits + status
        Git-->>Grounding: GitContext
    end
    Grounding-->>Routes: (soul_block, git_ctx, grounding_wall_ms)
    Routes->>Provider: OllamaCliProvider::new(model, Some(key))
    Note over Provider: Phase 1: no internal env read; key passed in
    Provider->>Cloud: POST /v1/messages (Authorization: Bearer)
    Cloud-->>Provider: SSE stream (thinking + text deltas)
    Provider-->>Routes: stream<Result<ProviderEvent>>
    Routes-->>Drawer: event: status_update {"text":"Calling ollama-cli …"}
    loop streaming
        Cloud-->>Provider: content_block_delta
        Provider-->>Routes: text(chunk)
        Routes-->>Drawer: event: text {"chunk":"…"}
    end
    Routes-->>Drawer: event: token_usage {input,output}
    Routes-->>Drawer: event: complete {reason:"complete"}
    Drawer-->>Operator: render assistant bubble + hide Thinking…
